"content\":\"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) Tasks\\n\\n**Module:** manifests  \\n**Language:** YAML  \\n**Size:** M  \\n**Stage:** ST-3 (completed)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Phase 1: WorkloadManager RBAC\\n\\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create WorkloadManager ServiceAccount\\n  - Set `apiVersion: v1`, `kind: ServiceAccount`\\n  - Name: `workloadmanager`\\n  - Set namespace to `{{ .Release.Namespace }}`\\n  - Add standard labels (optional)\\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`\\n  - Verify: `kubectl get sa/workloadmanager -n <namespace>` succeeds\\n\\n- [ ] **T1.2** Create WorkloadManager ClusterRole\\n  - Set `apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1`, `kind: ClusterRole`\\n  - Name: `workloadmanager`\\n  - Add rule for `agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxes`: full CRUD (get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete)\\n  - Add rule for `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxclaims`: full CRUD\\n  - Add rule for `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxtemplates`: full CRUD\\n  - Add rule for `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools`: full CRUD\\n  - Add rule for `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools/status`: get, update, patch\\n  - Add rule for `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters`: full CRUD\\n  - Add rule for `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/status`: get, update, patch\\n  - Add rule for `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/finalizers`: update\\n  - Add rule for `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes`: get, list, watch\\n  - Add rule for `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes/stat...\n  Line 23: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775880472200,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28547ee9affer1O2ZuAd3OZIbD\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ab97c03001VQ9lnVTJBaKeUC\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ab9691c001Dw8EyhXa9tsihb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28547ee9affer1O2ZuAd3OZIbD\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done! The tasks.md checklist for AR-031 has been written with atomic, independently verifiable tasks organized into 4 phases:\\n\\n- **Phase 1**: Wo