de-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-026/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z_logs/AR-018_ST-3.log:\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775880056717,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285516e0bffe2PWxVwG32DaMa0\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aaf48ff001NY03Xmof57U4il\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aaf2509001tZ60BWqPaXIOpS\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285516e0bffe2PWxVwG32DaMa0\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_functions.write:11\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/design.md\",\"content\":\"# AR-018 Design: Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n**AR ID:** AR-018  \\n**Module:** `pkg/agentd`  \\n**Language:** Go  \\n**Size:** S (Small)\\n\\nThe Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller is a Kubernetes controller that automatically deletes AgentRuntime resources that have exceeded their configured idle timeout. It monitors the `LastActivityTime` field in AgentRuntime status and compares it against the `IdleTimeoutSeconds` specified in the spec to determine when a resource should be cleaned up.\\n\\nThis implementation integrates with:\\n- **AgentRuntime API (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1)**: Watches AgentRuntime resources\\n- **client-go library**: Uses generated Kubernetes clientset for API interactions\\n- **controller-runtime**: Manages the controller lifecycle and reconciliation loop\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Architecture\\n\\n### High-Level Design\\n\\n```\\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\n│                         Kubernetes Cluster                                   │\\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\\n│  │                         AgentRuntime Resources                          │  │\\n│  │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐                    │  │\\n│  │  │  Runtime 1  │  │  Runtime 2  │  │  Runtime N  │                    │  │\\n│  │  │ (active)    │  │ (idle 20m)  │  │ (idle 45m)  │                    │  │\\n│  │  └──────┬──────┘  └──────┬──────┘  └──────┬──────┘                    │  │\\n│  │         │                │ ...\n  Line 29: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775880264277,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285516e0bffe2PWxVwG32DaMa0\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ab5dd69001ZqXrywU2sizTsO\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ab32fd1001HMZSQcvSJs2xI1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285516e0bffe2PWxVwG32DaMa0\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've successfully written the `design.md` file with comprehensive technical implementation details for AR-018 — Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller. \\n\\nThe design document includes:\\n\\n1. **Overview** — Introduction to the idle cleanup controller and its purpose\\n2. **Architecture** — High-level design diagrams showing the reconciliation flow and component interactions\\n3. **Directory Structure** — File organization for `pkg/agentd/` and `cmd/agentd/`\\n4. **Data Structures** — Complete type definitions including:\\n   - `Reconciler` with `Clock` interface for testability\\n   - `IdleTimeoutConfig` for timeout configuration\\n   - `CleanupResult` for cleanup decisions\\n   - `Metrics` for Prometheus integration\\n   - Configuration and constants\\n\\n5. **API Contracts** — Detailed interface specifications for:\\n   - `ReconcilerInterface.Reconcile()`\\n   - `CheckIdleTimeout()` function\\n   - `ExecuteCleanup()` function\\n   - Configuration and metrics functions\\n\\n6. **Error Handling** — Error categories, sentinel errors, `ReconcileError` structure, and error handling patterns\\n\\n7. **Testing Strategy** — Comprehensive unit tests including:\\n   - Reconciler tests (not found, no timeout, not expired, expired, no activity time)\\n   - `CheckIdleTimeout` tests\\n   - Config validation tests\\n   - Integration test examples\\n   - Test execution commands\\n\\n8. **Security Considerations** — RBAC requirements, time safety, logging safety\\n\\n9. **Performance Considerations** — Scalability targets, optimization strategies, resource usage\\n\\n10. **Integration Points** — How it integrates with AgentRuntime API, client-go, workload manager, and metrics\\n\\n11. **Dependencies** — Required Go packages and versions\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775880264273,\"end\":177588...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-035_ST-1.log:\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775880092641,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2854cfb41ffenZ5Bq5krRsBmly\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ab3b7ba001vlSBHVyJXjqd1g\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ab3b0a8001O8zmY9yrVHrgpr\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2854cfb41ffenZ5Bq5krRsBmly\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_d017d4fd56b243f58bcc6fc4\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"proposal.md\",\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/op