C 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) with 10 requirements and 60+ GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios covering:\\n\\n- **REQ-031.1**: ServiceAccount manifests (WorkloadManager, Router, Volcano Scheduler)\\n- **REQ-031.2**: ClusterRole manifests with detailed permissions\\n- **REQ-031.3**: ClusterRoleBinding manifests\\n- **REQ-031.4**: Namespace-scoped Role manifests (Router)\\n- **REQ-031.5**: RoleBinding manifests\\n- **REQ-031.6**: Namespace management\\n- **REQ-031.7**: Combined RBAC manifest\\n- **REQ-031.8**: RBAC validation and verification\\n- **REQ-031.9**: Multi-namespace support\\n- **REQ-031.10**: RBAC cleanup\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775880079768,\"end\":1775880079768}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-035_ST-0.log:\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775879994947,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2854dd4ddffe3Poa1Vw4IwdTwH\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ab23929001O6ofpyY9Z0cWyh\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ab22c1c0015h0BJBah1rzHHY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2854dd4ddffe3Poa1Vw4IwdTwH\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_e66489ee837b43738e6c9d44\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"changes/**/*\",\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/design.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ch