1BR4R\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aaf9e8c001OZ8ebifl6qD3ZT\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_a5fa8dda125b416fbd0a845e\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) Tasks\\n2: \\n3: ## Implementation Tasks\\n4: \\n5: - [ ] Define ServiceAccount manifests\\n6: - [ ] Define Role manifests\\n7: - [ ] Define RoleBinding manifests\\n8: - [ ] Validate RBAC configuration\\n9: \\n10: ## Notes\\n\\n(End of file - total 10 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) Tasks\\n\\n## Implementation Tasks\\n\\n- [ ] Define ServiceAccount manifests\\n- [ ] Define Role manifests\\n- [ ] Define RoleBinding manifests\\n- [ ] Validate RBAC configuration\\n\\n## Notes\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[]},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775879828356,\"end\":1775879828365}}}}\n  Line 24: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775879832497,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aafc224001hs1L0KrYZVMtvP\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aafb3bd0017U5i6r3VyFEaJ0\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I have all the context needed. Let me write the proposal.md for AR-031:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775879832495,\"end\":1775879832495}}}\n  Line 25: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775879919425,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aafc3b2001FSyCS2QDRRMPR0\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aafb3bd0017U5i6r3VyFEaJ0\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_4c30c672d5594fd0aee472be\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 RBAC 配置，将 ServiceAccount、Role/ClusterRole、RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding 从 Helm Chart 模板中独立出来，形成可单独部署的 RBAC 配置模块。该 RBAC 配置是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的权限管理基础，支撑 Workload Manager 和 Router 的访问控制需求。\\n\\n目标是：\\n\\n1. **权限最小化** - 为每个组件分配精确的 RBAC 权限，遵循 least privilege 原则\\n2. **模块化部署** - RBAC 配置可独立于 Helm Chart 单独部署，支持预创建权限\\n3. **多租户支持** - 通过 Role/RoleBinding 支持 namespace-scoped 权限，实现多租户隔离\\n4. **审计友好** - 独立的 RBAC 配置便于权限审计和安全审查\\n5. **环境兼容性** - 支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化权限配置\\n\\n本实现基于 manifests/design.md 和 manifests/delta-spec.md 的规范，遵循 Kubernetes RBAC 最佳实践。\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n**Module:** manifests  \\n**Language:** YAML  \\n**Size:** M\\n\\n本 AR 包含：\\n\\n- **包含内容：**\\n  - Workload Manager ServiceAccount 定义\\n  - Workload Manager ClusterRole 定义（cluster-wide 权限）\\n  - Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding 定义\\n  - Router ServiceAccount 定义（可选）\\n  - Router Role 定义（namespace-scoped 权限，可选）\\n  - Router RoleBinding 定义（可选）\\n  - RBAC 配置验证脚本\\n  - 使用文档和权限说明\\n\\n- **不包含内容：**\\n  - Helm Chart 模板（由 AR-030 管理）\\n  - Kubernetes 集群配置\\n  - 应用层代码修改\\n  - 认证/授权逻辑实现\\n\\n## Current State Analysis\\n\\n### 现有 RBAC 配置\\n\\n根据 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`：\\n- Workload Manager ServiceAccount 已定义\\n- Workload Manager ClusterRole 已定义，包含完整的 CRD、Pods、Secrets 权限\\n- Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding 已定义\\n\\n根据 `manifests/design.md`：\\n- Router RBAC 设计为可选的 namespace-scoped Role + RoleBinding\\n- Router 默认不创建 RBAC，通过 `router.rbac.create` 控制\\n\\n### 参考设计规范\\n\\n根据 `manifests/delta-spec.md` REQ-030.5 和 REQ-030.6：\\n\\n**Workload Manager RBAC 要求：**\\n- ServiceAccount: `workloadmanager`，位于 release namespace\\n- ClusterRole: `wo...\n  Line 28: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775879925497,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ab12248001eIb9M6Qj6jll2v\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ab11786001PJ7VaRZE0bTG3S\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550ae7cffeJCKMMIUVtTBgNm\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Written `changes/AR-031/proposal.md` with:\\n\\n- **Purpose**: Independent RBAC configuration module for ServiceAccount/Role/Binding, supporting pre-creation and audit\\n- **Scope**: WorkloadManager (ClusterRole) + Router (namespace-scoped Role, optional), Kustomize config, validation script\\n- **Current State Analysis**: Existing Helm templates in AR-030, gaps identified (no standalone RBAC, missing audit support)\\n- **Proposed Changes**: Modular directory structure with separate YAML files, kustomization.yaml, validation script\\n- **Impact Analysis**: Dependencies (Kubernetes ≥1.21, kubectl, Kustomize), relationship with AR-030\\n- **Alternatives Considered**: Helm-only RBAC, Operator-based, single-file, ClusterRole vs Role tradeoffs\\n- **Testing/Acceptance**: `kubectl auth can-i` verification, isolation tests, deployment validation\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775879925495,\"end\":1775879925495}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-037_ST-2.log:\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775879817229,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550e39affe44ngNC3XoJfwct\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aaf86650014QIg0ny7344SLq\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aaf7824001dBaZKTaRHSnWH3\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28550e39affe44ngNC3XoJfwct\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_4deac0ab42394c13a1c850d9\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/*delta*.md\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-037/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-036/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260