entcube, version 0.1.0)\\n- `values.yaml` - Configuration for Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano Scheduler\\n- `crds/agentruntimes.yaml` - AgentRuntime CRD\\n- `crds/codeinterpreters.yaml` - CodeInterpreter CRD with status subresource\\n\\n**Templates:**\\n- `agentcube-router.yaml` - Deployment + Service with health probes, WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\\n- `workloadmanager.yaml` - Deployment + Service with Redis integration\\n- `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` - ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\\n- `rbac-router.yaml` - Conditional Router RBAC (controlled by `router.rbac.create`)\\n- `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` - Optional Volcano Scheduler with ConfigMap\\n\\n**Tests (unittest):**\\n- `agentcube-router_test.yaml` - 8 test scenarios\\n- `workloadmanager_test.yaml` - 8 test scenarios\\n- `rbac-router_test.yaml` - RBAC toggle tests\\n- `workloadmanager-rbac_test.yaml` - WorkloadManager RBAC tests\\n- `volcano-scheduler_test.yaml` - Volcano scheduler tests\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Deferred\\n\\n**Missing Files (per design.md/delta-spec.md):**\\n- `.helmignore` - Packaging exclusion patterns\\n- `templates/_helpers.tpl` - Template helper functions\\n- `templates/redis-secret.yaml` - Redis password Secret (REDIS_PASSWORD currently uses values directly)\\n\\n**Design Spec Gaps:**\\n- Chart.yaml missing: keywords, maintainers, home, sources fields\\n- Router uses direct password value instead of Secret reference\\n- No `router.config` field implementation in values.yaml\\n- No multi-environment values files (values-dev.yaml, values-prod.yaml)\\n\\n**Open Questions from Spec (unresolved):**\\n1. External Redis Operator...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-034_ST-5.log:\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775879579443,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2855687fcffeNYLesVAG34165B\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aabe59f001sHI0Ue9E16s45b\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aabd88b001fSCStQS6PJfn2T\",\"sessionID\":