pirationTimeout` (15 minutes)\\n4. **Efficient Requeueing**: Scheduling reconciliation at the exact expiration time to minimize unnecessary API calls\\n5. **Error Handling**: Graceful handling of parse errors, not-found errors, and deletion failures\\n6. **Binary Integration**: A standalone `agentd` binary that runs the controller using controller-runtime manager\\n\\nThis controller integrates with the agentcube platform to ensure sandboxes don't consume resources indefinitely when idle, complementing the workload manager's sandbox creation and session management capabilities.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n| Item | Detail |\\n|------|--------|\\n| **Reconciler** | controller-runtime `Reconciler` implementation for Sandbox resources |\\n| **Idle ...\n  Line 32: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775879588054,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28556d22bffevyS1U2GDohG19W\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aabe2dc001UYYIqIGUnl0WYj\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aabb9c1001TiP8x4aYrXxoVh\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28556d22bffevyS1U2GDohG19W\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've successfully written the `proposal.md` for AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器. The proposal follows the same format and structure as the existing AR-017 proposal and includes:\\n\\n**Key sections covered:**\\n\\n1. **Purpose** — Overview of the idle cleanup controller and its six main deliverables\\n2. **Scope** — In-scope items (Reconciler, Idle Detection, Resource Deletion, etc.) and out-of-scope items (activity tracking, custom timeouts, etc.)\\n3. **Design** — File structure, architecture diagram, reconciliation flow diagram, and core type definitions\\n4. **Execution Flows** — Four detailed flow sequences (successful cleanup, future expiration, parse error recovery, binary startup)\\n5. **Error Handling** — Error types and result/error mapping table\\n6. **Security Considerations** — RBAC requirements, annotation trust, and resource cleanup patterns\\n7. **Impact Analysis** — Files created, dependencies, downstream consumers, performance characteristics, and watched resources\\n8. **Alternatives Considered** — Four alternatives evaluated (CronJob-based, OwnerReference TTL, Webhook validation, Workload Manager handling)\\n9. **Risks and Mitigations** — Risk table with likelihood, impact, and mitigation strategies\\n10. **Verification** — Unit tests, integration tests, manual verification commands, and test scenarios\\n11. **References** — Links to design docs, specs, and related documentation\\n12. **Success Criteria** — 12 verifiable success criteria\\n\\nThe proposal references the existing `idle-cleanup/design.md` and `idle-cleanup/spec.md` documents for detailed implementation guidance, and integrates with the `client-go` patterns from the agentcube project.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775879588050,\"end\":1775879588050}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-030_ST-5.log:\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775879181632,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2855a9203ffebYGUS0ExwEQGNY\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aa5ca83001Ud22kC03M2X27V\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aa5be84001d4n8YNIGr1QujP\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2855a9203ffebYGUS0ExwEQGNY\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_cc671f8ee29540e68d732cb3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Deployment Design\\n2: \\n3: Source tree: `/tmp/agentcube-ref` (reference clone). Paths below are relative to repository root unless noted.\\n4: \\n5: ## Chart.yaml\\n6: \\n7: | Field | Value |\\n8: |--------|--------|\\n9: | `apiVersion` | `v1` |\\n10: | `name` | `agentcube` |\\n11: | `description` | `A Helm chart for AgentCube` |\\n12: | `version` | `0.1.0` |\\n13: | `appVersion` | `1.0.0` |\\n14: \\n15: ## values.yaml — full key tree (type & default)\\n16: \\n17: | Path | Type | Defaul