ncode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-030_ST-2.log:\n  Line 24: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775878691331,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2856236b1ffec1k4q3sY0kVI6Z\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a9e4fdf001IAYlWHwAO7ilFL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a9e3eb0001k0IxGIrlMyalXi\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2856236b1ffec1k4q3sY0kVI6Z\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_9ad6479ff1a343e291a6fdac\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Helm Chart 模板与 Values 配置，提供标准的 Kubernetes 部署能力。该 Helm Chart 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的核心部署载体，支撑 Workload Manager、Router、以及可选的 Volcano Agent Scheduler 的安装与管理。\\n6: \\n7: 目标是：\\n8: \\n9: 1. **标准化部署流程** - 通过 Helm Chart 统一控制平面组件的部署配置，支持一键安装/升级\\n10: 2. **配置灵活性** - 通过 values.yaml 提供完整的配置项，支持镜像、资源、副本数等自定义\\n11: 3. **CRD 生命周期管理** - 将 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 纳入 Chart 管理，随 Chart 安装\\n12: 4. **Redis 连接配置** - 支持 Redis 地址和认证的灵活配置，满足 Workload Manager 和 Router 运行时需求\\n13: 5. **可选组件支持** - 支持 Router RBAC、Volcano Scheduler 等可选组件的按需启用\\n14: 6. **多环境兼容** - 通过 values 覆盖支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化配置\\n15: \\n16: 本实现基于 deployment/spec.md 和 deployment/design.md 的规范，遵循 Helm 3 最佳实践。\\n17: \\n18: ## Scope\\n19: \\n20: **Module:** manifests  \\n21: **Language:** YAML  \\n22: **Size:** L\\n23: \\n24: 本 AR 包含：\\n25: \\n26: - **包含内容：**\\n27:   - Chart.yaml 实现（apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0）\\n28:   - values.yaml 完整配置树（Redis、Router、WorkloadManager、Volcano Scheduler）\\n29:   - Workload Manager Deployment 和 Service 模板\\n30:   - Router Deployment 和 Service 模板\\n31:   - Workload Manager RBAC 资源（ServiceAccount、ClusterRole、ClusterRoleBinding）\\n32:   - Router 可选 RBAC 资源（ServiceAccount、Role、RoleBinding）\\n33:   - Volcano Agent Scheduler 可选资源（ServiceAccount、ConfigMap、ClusterRole、ClusterRoleBinding、Se...\n  Line 29: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775878846584,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2856236b1ffec1k4q3sY0kVI6Z\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a9e6a0b001LAvg5tDU273KqK\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a9e5a3b001sl32K3eWAu27wV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2856236b1ffec1k4q3sY0kVI6Z\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_784e5e4aa30a47b4a8ad25da\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/delta-spec.md\",\"content\":\"# Delta Specification — AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n**Module:** `manifests`  \\n**Language:** YAML  \\n**Size:** L  \\n**Type:** Helm Chart implementation for AgentCube control plane components\\n\\n**Base Specs:** deployment/spec.md, deployment/design.md\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Requirements & Scenarios\\n\\n### REQ-030.1: Chart.yaml Metadata\\n\\n**Requirement:** The system SHALL implement Chart.yaml with apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0, and appVersion 1.0.0.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Chart.yaml structure\\n- **GIVEN** the Helm chart is initialized\\n- **WHEN** Chart.yaml is created\\n- **THEN** it SHALL contain:\\n  - `apiVersion: v1`\\n  - `name: agentcube`\\n  - `description: A Helm chart for AgentCube`\\n  - `version: 0.1.0`\\n  - `appVersion: \\\"1.0.0\\\"`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Chart metadata keywords\\n- **GIVEN** Chart.yaml is created\\n- **WHEN** metadata is defined\\n- **THEN** keywords SHALL include: `agent`, `sandbox`, `kubernetes`, `volcano`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Chart maintainers\\n- **GIVEN** Chart.yaml is created\\n- **WHEN** maintainers are defined\\n- **THEN** maintainers SHALL include Volcano Authors with email `volcano-sh@googlegroups.com`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Chart home and sources\\n- **GIVEN** Chart.yaml is created\\n- **WHEN** home and sources are defined\\n- **THEN** they SHALL reference `https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\\n\\n---\\n\\n### REQ-030.2: values.yaml Configuration Tree\\n\\n**Requirement:** The system SHALL implement values.yaml with complete configuration tree for Redis, Router, ...\n  Line 32: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775878856155,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2856236b1ffec1k4q3sY0kVI6Z\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7aa0ced7001k1wFioLdE67LKx\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7aa0b8b10013qblwno2EgJeEb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2856236b1ffec1k4q3sY0kVI6Z\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done. Created `manifests/delta-spec.md` with 474 lines covering all AR-030 requirements in OpenSpec format with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios.\\n\\nThe spec includes:\\n- **REQ-030.1**: Chart.yaml metadata\\n- **REQ-030.2**: values.yaml configuration tree (Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano)\\n- **REQ-030.3**: Workload Manager Deployment template\\n- **REQ-030.4**: Router Deployment template\\n- **REQ-030.5**: Workload Manager RBAC\\n- **REQ-030.6**: Router RBAC (optional)\\n- **REQ-030.7**: Volcano Agent Scheduler (optional)\\n- **REQ-030.8**: Redis Secret template\\n- **REQ-030.9**: CRD files\\n- **REQ-030.10**: .helmignore\\n- **REQ-030.11**: Helm lint/template validation\\n- **REQ-030.12**: Multi-environment support\\n\\nNote: The LSP errors shown are in the existing CRD file (`agentruntime.yaml`), not in the spec I created.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775878856153,\"end\":1775878856153}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-034_ST-2.log:\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775878508466,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285647e18ffeoctb678uOjeElq\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a9b8e2a001lbma4d4sw4PZL7\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a9b82c4001YbRXWt4TcDlqjd\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285647e18ffeoctb678uOjeElq\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_eeb617c29d8b403d8fe4ad2b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\