b83c0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/deployment/spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/deployment/spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Deployment Specification\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: Deploy AgentCube control-plane components (Workload Manager, Router), optional Volcano agent scheduler, and required Redis connectivity via the `agentcube` Helm chart, container images, and Makefile-driven builds.\\n5: \\n6: ## Requirements\\n7: \\n8: ### Requirement: Helm chart installation\\n9: The system SHALL support installing/upgrading the AgentCube stack with Helm from `manifests/charts/base`, including namespace creation and values for Redis, images, replicas, and optional router RBAC.\\n10: \\n11: #### Scenario: Install with release namespace\\n12: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster and Helm 3 available\\n13: - **WHEN** the operator runs `helm upgrade --install <release> manifests/charts/base --namespace <ns> --create-namespace` with required `redis.addr` (and optional `redis.password`) plus component image overrides as needed\\n14: - **THEN** chart templates apply Workload Manager and Router workloads (and optional Volcano resources when enabled) in `<ns>` without manual editing of rendered YAML\\n15: \\n16: ### Requirement: Helm values and Redis connectivity\\n17: The system SHALL require Redis address configuration for Workload Manager and Router at runtime via chart values `redis.addr` and `redis.password` (empty password permitted when Redis has no auth).\\n18: \\n19: #### Scenario: Compon...\n  Line 42: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775878501199,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285657736ffe8iRmYVhOjRoQPi\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a9b6eaf001OZn4mHXQAhH3mk\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a9b4ec2001dl9uwAtvu2r4Bl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285657736ffe8iRmYVhOjRoQPi\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_174d40c7076a45238de7c510\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/deployment/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/deployment/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Deployment Design\\n2: \\n3: Source tree: `/tmp/agentcube-ref` (reference clone). Paths below are relative to repository root unless noted.\\n4: \\n5: ## Chart.yaml\\n6: \\n7: | Field | Value |\\n8: |--------|--------|\\n9: | `apiVersion` | `v1` |\\n10: | `name` | `agentcube` |\\n11: | `description` | `A Helm chart for AgentCube` |\\n12: | `version` | `0.1.0` |\\n13: | `appVersion` | `1.0.0` |\\n14: \\n15: ## values.yaml — full key tree (type & default)\\n16: \\n17: | Path | Type | Default |\\n18: |------|------|---------|\\n19: | `imagePullSecrets` | array | `[]` |\\n20: | `nameOverride` | string | `\\\"\\\"` |\\n21: | `fullnameOverride` | string | `\\\"\\\"` |\\n22: | `redis.addr` | string | `\\\"\\\"` |\\n23: | `redis.password` | string | `\\\"\\\"` |\\n24: | `router.replicas` | int | `1` |\\n25: | `router.image.repository` | string | `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router` |\\n26: | `router.image.pullPolicy` | string | `IfNotPresent` |\\n27: | `router.image.tag` | string | `latest` |\\n28: | `router.service.type` | string | `ClusterIP` |\\n29: | `router.service.port` | int | `8080` |\\n30: | `router.service.targetPort` | int | `8080` |\\n31: | `router.resources.limits.cpu` | string | `500m` |\\n32: | `router.resources.limits.memory` | string | `512Mi` |\\n33: | `router.resources.requests.cpu` | string | `100m` |\\n34: | `router.resources.requests.memory` | string | `128Mi` |\\n...\n  Line 46: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775878640192,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285657736ffe8iRmYVhOjRoQPi\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a9b8c63001RoWCXqvLmSYy2Y\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a9b73890010XG5qi4Y1czrQm\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285657736ffe8iRmYVhOjRoQPi\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_21690f1ffbd940a3b7ce80fd\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Helm Chart 模板与 Values 配置，提供标准的 Kubernetes 部署能力。该 Helm Chart 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的核心部署载体，支撑 Workload Manager、Router、以及可选的 Volcano Agent Scheduler 的安装与管理。\\n\\n目标是：\\n\\n1. **标准化部署流程** - 通过 Helm Chart 统一控制平面组件的部署配置，支持一键安装/升级\\n2. **配置灵活性** - 通过 values.yaml 提供完整的配置项，支持镜像、资源、副本数等自定义\\n3. **CRD 生命周期管理** - 将 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 纳入 Chart 管理，随 Chart 安装\\n4. **Redis 连接配置** - 支持 Redis 地址和认证的灵活配置，满足 Workload Manager 和 Router 运行时需求\\n5. **可选组件支持** - 支持 Router RBAC、Volcano Scheduler 等可选组件的按需启用\\n6. **多环境兼容** - 通过 values 覆盖支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化配置\\n\\n本实现基于 deployment/spec.md 和 deployment/design.md 的规范，遵循 Helm 3 最佳实践。\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n**Module:** manifests  \\n**Language:** YAML  \\n**Size:** L\\n\\n本 AR 包含：\\n\\n- **包含内容：**\\n  - Chart.yaml 实现（apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0）\\n  - values.yaml 完整配置树（Redis、Router、WorkloadManager、Volcano Scheduler）\\n  - Workload Manager Deployment 和 Service 模板\\n  - Router Deployment 和 Service 模板\\n  - Workload Manager RBAC 资源（ServiceAccount、ClusterRole、ClusterRoleBinding）\\n  - Router 可选 RBAC 资源（ServiceAccount、Role、RoleBinding）\\n  - Volcano Agent Scheduler 可选资源（ServiceAccount、ConfigMap、ClusterRole、ClusterRoleBinding、Service、Deployment）\\n  - CRD 文件（agentruntimes、codeinterpreters）\\n  - .helmignore 文件\\n  - 单元测试（values 验证、模板渲染测试）\\n  - 安装文档和使用示例\\n\\n- **不包含内容：**\\n  - Docker 镜像构建（由 docker/Dockerfile 单独管理）\\n  - Redis 集群部署（作为外部依赖）\\n  - 应用层代码修改\\n  - 客户端 SDK 或 CLI 工具\\n\\n## Current State Analysis\\n\\n### 现有 manifests 结构\\n\\n根据 `manifests/charts/base/` 目录：\\n- `crds/agentruntime.yaml` 已存在，包含 AgentRuntime CRD 定义\\n- 缺少 CodeInterpreter CRD\\n- 缺少 Chart.yaml、val...\n  Line 49: {\